{% if sub_agents %}

## Available Sub-Agents
You can delegate tasks to specialized sub-agents:
{% for sub_agent in sub_agents %}

<description_of_sub_agent:{{sub_agent.name}}>
### {{ sub_agent.name }}
{{ sub_agent.description or 'Specialized agent for ' + sub_agent.name + '-related tasks' }}
Usage:
<tool_use>
  <tool_name>Agent</tool_name>
  <parameter>
    <sub_agent_name>{{sub_agent.name}}</sub_agent_name>
    <message>task description</message>
  </parameter>
</tool_use>
</description_of_sub_agent:{{sub_agent.name}}>
{% endfor %}
{% endif %}
